court: IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY
judgment_text:
IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY

CIVIL APPELLATE JURISDICTION CAUSE TITLES & APPEARANCES AS NOTIFIED ...... P.C. P.C. P.C. 1. As per office noting, these matters are not traceable. 2. Office to take necessary steps including to reconstruct the record within one week from today and report compliance. If necessary, Office shall call upon the Advocates appearing in the respective matters to furnish relevant missing documents. 3. Place all these matters on 19th September : 2 : under caption direction . 4. Copy of this order be forwarded to the Registrar (Judicial) as well as the Registrar General forthwith to ensure that necessary steps are taken in time, as the matters, if pending, cannot brook delay as they pertain to years 1991 and 1992. A.M.KHANWILKAR, J.
